import React from "react";
import {Container, Navbar, DropdownButton, Dropdown, NavDropdown, Image, Row, Col} from "react-bootstrap";

class NavigationBar extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Navbar bg="dark" variant={"dark"} expand="lg">
                <Container>
                    <Row >
                        <Col >
                            <Image src="classroom.png" rounded height="70" width="70"/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <DropdownButton id="dropdown-basic-button" title="Actions">
                                <Dropdown.Item href="#/action-1">Action</Dropdown.Item>
                            </DropdownButton>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Navbar.Brand href="/classroom">Welcome to the Classroom</Navbar.Brand>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <NavDropdown title="Username" id="nav-dropdown">
                                <NavDropdown.Item href="/logout">Log Out</NavDropdown.Item>
                            </NavDropdown>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        )
    }
}

export default NavigationBar;
